    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Loretta's Mastery</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Loretta's Mastery" src="/file/Elden-Ring/lorettas_mastery_sorcery_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="lorettas mastery sorcery elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Loretta's Sorceries" href="/Loretta's+Sorceries" target="">Loretta's Sorceries</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost&nbsp;39</td> 
     <td>Slots Used&nbsp;1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Fires four great arrow from a magic greatbow at once 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;46 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a> 0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Loretta's Mastery</strong> is a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceries" href="/Sorceries" target="">Sorcery</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Loretta's Mastery spell,</strong> unlike the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Loretta's Greatbow" href="/Loretta's+Greatbow" target="">Loretta's Greatbow</a>&nbsp;that shoots one arrow from a magic greatbow, this Sorcery fires four great arrows at once. Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Sorcery used by Loretta, Knight of the Haligtree.<br> <br>Creates a magic greatbow and fires four great arrows simultaneously. <br>Charging enhances potency. Hold to keep the great arrows nocked.<br> <br>Developed by Loretta after her long, bloody journey to seek out a place where the Albinaurics could live in peace. <br></em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Loretta's Mastery</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Loretta's Mastery</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Loretta, Knight of the Haligtree" href="/Loretta,+Knight+of+the+Haligtree">Loretta, Knight of the Haligtree</a> upon defeat. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=4629&amp;lat=-44.76719&amp;lng=150.63072&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=4629&amp;lat=-44.76719&amp;lng=150.63072&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<div style="max-width: 560px; max-height: 316px;"> 
 <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"> 
  <div id="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gqSzUthyrsU" class="embed-responsive-item youtube-item" style="display: flex; justify-content: center;"> 
